    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. This beauty has been such a reliable ride for me, and I\u2019ve truly loved every mile in it. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like an absolute dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
