    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six mated to a Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This A80 chassis is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, retaining its factory sequential turbo plumbing and Torsen limited-slip differential. The engine pulls strongly with consistent boost pressure, and the gearbox exhibits precise gate entry with healthy synchros. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and a cooling system overhaul. While the paint and interior show light signs of honest use, the vehicle remains structurally excellent and free of common subframe fatigue. A prime candidate for the purist seeking a high-performance JDM icon that is ready for the open road.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
