    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a well-cared-for example that perfectly balances performance and daily usability. The exterior finish presents beautifully with a deep luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a vehicle that has been enjoyed on the open road. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery shows only light creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats throughout its life. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium sound system and sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a comprehensive logbook available for review. The engine runs smoothly without any hesitation, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This is a solid, honest vehicle that requires nothing but a new driver to get behind the wheel.",
      "price": 29800.0,
