      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an expertly maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic discipline. This unit has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes consistent performance and a refined presence on the road. All systems have been thoroughly evaluated to ensure they meet our exacting standards for reliability and longevity. This is a distinguished opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances sophisticated engineering with enduring value.",
